RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 1 6F Dirt CR: 91. Allowance Purse 10780. FOR FOUR YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD. Weight, 123 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since January 12 Allowed 2 lbs. A Race Since December 27 Allowed 4 lbs. A Race Since November 27 Allowed 7 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: ICATIRO stalked pace, rallied, driving. SUPER KOJAK late gain. SOPE bid, flattened out. EMAJESTIN chased, weakened. JESS'S STRIDE close up, weakened.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 2 6 1/2F Dirt CR: 42. Maiden Special Weight Purse 10780. FOR MAIDENS, THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 120 lbs.; Older, 123 lbs. Inferiores y debutantes Allowed 4 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: PULPMASTER led throughout. DON DANY R. gamely between horses. KEEN CAUSEWAY off pace, late kick. BRING IT ON failed to menace. GREAT AZABACHE chased, weakened.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 3 1 1/16M Dirt CR: 53. Claiming Purse 6000. FOR NATIVE FOUR YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NEVER WON FIVE RACES AND WHICH HAVE STARTED FOR A CLAIMING PRICE OF $8,000 OR LESS. Weight, 120 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since January 12 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since December 27 Allowed 2 lbs. A Race Since November 27 Allowed 4 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: QUEQUE up in final strides. BACONAO off slowly, bid, dueled, gamely. CARTILLERO close up, bid, dueled, gamely. MILO ALBERTO close up, bid. QUE BUENO ES chased, weakened. HERALDO failed to menace.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 4 6 1/2F Dirt CR: 77. Claiming Purse 7350. FOR FILLIES AND MARES FOUR YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Weight, 123 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since January 12 Allowed 2 lbs. A Race Since December 27 Allowed 4 lbs. A Race Since November 27 Allowed 7 lbs. Claiming Price $14,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: SILENT RAIN up in final strides. WEST LOVE finished well. EYE CENTRAL vied for lead, gave way. ITSMYLUCKYGIRL improved position. SURF SPA pressed pace, weakened.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 5 6 1/2F Dirt CR: 67. Claiming Purse 6000. FOR FILLIES AND MARES FOUR YEARS OLD AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NOT WON THREE RACES SINCE JANUARY 1. Weight, 121 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since July 30 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since July 15 Allowed 3 lbs. A Race Since June 15 Allowed 5 lbs. Claiming Price $4, 000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: RENEESDREAMGIRL drew clear. MYSTICAL JUSTICE second best. OUR CHOICE close up, gamely. WANDY EXPRESS bid, lacked. CYBERICA close up, evenly. MEET ME HALF WAY close up, weakened. ROMANTIC MELODY weakened. CAPTURED PRIZE improved position. CHAPECOENSE failed to menace. TIUNA off slowly. SAICHIMANA dropped back. FANTASY TALE failed to menace.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 6 5 1/2F Dirt CR: 65. Claiming Purse 6000. FOR FILLIES AND MARES FOUR YEARS OLD AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NEVER WON THREE RACES AND WHICH HAVE STARTED FOR A CLAIMING PRICE OF $8,000 OR LESS. Weight, 121 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since January 12 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since December 27 Allowed 3 lbs. A Race Since November 27 Allowed 5 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: RUNNERS DREAM dueled, prevailed. SUNTANA late kick. DAMA RADIANTE vied for lead, dueled. BUSTIN DISCO close up, some late gain. FOREVER COMERIO mild rally, weakened. LUNA FORTUNA stalked pace, weakened. PRETTY DOCTOR close up, weakened. CHEN'S CLEANSHADOW failed to menace. SUNSHINE BAR failed to menace. BAHAMIAN BEAUTY lame, did not finish.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 7 6F Dirt CR: 9. Maiden Claiming Purse 6000. FOR NATIVE MAIDENS, FILLIES AND MARES THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 118 lbs.; Older, 121 lbs. Clasif. $4,000 y debutantes Allowed 2 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: AZONDRA dueled, driving. ANTOFAGASTA second best, good effort. KPULINA close up, mild rally. AMAYA BESITO close up, weakened. LA CHAMPA bad start. ADIVINADORA off slowly, no menace. WIN FAVIOLA vied for lead, weakened. NAHIARA ZOE lame, did not finish.
